title: Zan vs. Zan
description:
This is a real photo, not a photoshop composite! Zan Moore is spinning flowtoys' double light staves.
Strobist info: Two-second exposure with both front and rear curtain flash to get the two images of Zan. Radio-triggered Sunpak 622's firing into umbrellas camera right and left, with a third bare Sunpak 622 in the background camera left providing rim lighting. [098124]
